{"tid":1690341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"試下學識將仇恨放係心入面","createTime":"2019-11-03T09:27:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T17:04:46.000Z","uid":90615,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e1b0bff395fe2e1f804834f5c634a950c99df75d","tid":1690341,"uid":90615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:27:48.000Z","msg":"香港人好容易有阿Q精神既補償心理<br />\n黑警殺人非禮強姦濫暴<br />\n大家係會嬲 即時會係ig fb comment黑警死全家<br />\n再即刻參加街坊look屌狗等活動<br />\n但呢啲行為只會令你自我感覺良好<br />\n覺得自己做左野然後沾沾<br />\n咁樣對黑警係0殺傷力<br />\n<br />\n今日開始試下將仇恨放入心底<br />\n唔洗日日屌 見到狗用正常態度<br />\n將仇恨壓係心底 由佢慢慢發大<br />\n如果大家都有呢種壓抑<br />\n好快就會有唔同既事發生"},{"pid":"e00c6627bdab3ceb81d94a3e0535f04cbf2dce43","tid":1690341,"uid":252064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:57:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vc3yrVa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVc3yrVa.jpg&h=3023c79d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n岩也 做實事要理智咁去思考<br />\n情緒只係推動去做既其中一個原因"},{"pid":"25e6aa03d8b289eea4b5089d28a8d8b84331e9ef","tid":1690341,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T17:00:57.000Z","msg":"放棄"},{"pid":"f173e766de86cb419dec50183f9a113c3a3ca8e2","tid":1690341,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T17:04:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}